{"id": "ChIJw3k8iZ5-hYARJSkLTdSXbls", "rating": 4.3, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_EXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 1490, "displayName": {"text": "Comal", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Modern design & Mexican cuisine meet at this eatery known for its cocktails & vibrant outdoor area.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJw3k8iZ5-hYARJSkLTdSXbls/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25RdExWRlliMEpxT0dKaE16WlNiSGhFWVU0NWFYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Was pleasantly surprised by the atmosphere of the back area of Comal. From the front, it doesn’t really look that big but once your inside they an elegant sit down interior and then their back area has a tall ceiling and a very earthy vibe with a bar connected. The food itself is authentic. Especially their hand pressed tortillas. The prices are a bit steep but it’s worth it for a cute dinner date or elegant time with the family.  I got the cod tacos which were extremely delicious. The tortillas are super soft and surprisingly light.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Was pleasantly surprised by the atmosphere of the back area of Comal. From the front, it doesn’t really look that big but once your inside they an elegant sit down interior and then their back area has a tall ceiling and a very earthy vibe with a bar connected. The food itself is authentic. Especially their hand pressed tortillas. The prices are a bit steep but it’s worth it for a cute dinner date or elegant time with the family.  I got the cod tacos which were extremely delicious. The tortillas are super soft and surprisingly light.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Aryan", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116558895713583844872/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeEU1649J6GwNyCOS176FWJ6Ah3PnmAzKgY2bTmNHaPshl1SUc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-06-22T19:58:02.744038984Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25RdExWRlliMEpxT0dKaE16WlNiSGhFWVU0NWFYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25RdExWRlliMEpxT0dKaE16WlNiSGhFWVU0NWFYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857e9e893c79c3:0x5b6e97d44d0b2925"}, {"name": "places/ChIJw3k8iZ5-hYARJSkLTdSXbls/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xSQmEzbGFla014WjI1UFptSkhVVWsxY0ZCTFMxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "11 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This upscale Mexican restaurant has amazing vibes and delicious food. We sat inside, but there's a really pretty shaded outdoor bar area with heaters that looked really nice too. The service was attentive, the food was very flavorful and felt like just enough to feel satisfied, but not so much you're struggling to finish.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This upscale Mexican restaurant has amazing vibes and delicious food. We sat inside, but there's a really pretty shaded outdoor bar area with heaters that looked really nice too. The service was attentive, the food was very flavorful and felt like just enough to feel satisfied, but not so much you're struggling to finish.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Chloe", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109002821951708265678/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlnnYSMR92BvTtwUfq3SkiE_ZBBPEg-9KJN7j9S4_IlWIxgDHp=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-08-08T06:01:52.747495493Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xSQmEzbGFla014WjI1UFptSkhVVWsxY0ZCTFMxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xSQmEzbGFla014WjI1UFptSkhVVWsxY0ZCTFMxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857e9e893c79c3:0x5b6e97d44d0b2925"}, {"name": "places/ChIJw3k8iZ5-hYARJSkLTdSXbls/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNucmV2QWxRRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Had a lovely dinner there last night. Our waitress was very attentive. We had the whole roasted chicken and it came with lovely tortillas, beans and rice. Cocktails were yummy too. I liked the ceviche, though there could’ve been more shrimp. The Tlayuda was very good. Also, there were a lot of adorable children running around, which is always a plus.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Had a lovely dinner there last night. Our waitress was very attentive. We had the whole roasted chicken and it came with lovely tortillas, beans and rice. Cocktails were yummy too. I liked the ceviche, though there could’ve been more shrimp. The Tlayuda was very good. Also, there were a lot of adorable children running around, which is always a plus.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alethea D", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111818573240544302530/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV71oIP9EVRpzovrb82kKvYkVU0WO_TREi3xFBT9mGHMHLhZjwC=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2024-09-28T16:16:56.489964Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNucmV2QWxRRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNucmV2QWxRRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857e9e893c79c3:0x5b6e97d44d0b2925"}, {"name": "places/ChIJw3k8iZ5-hYARJSkLTdSXbls/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xrelYxTkxhbWM1YWxSYVdFeDFjbHBHWjBsUWRIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Alex and Jose at the outdoor bar totally made our experience!! We enjoyed the Comal Swizzle and whole cod! Felt like in a different tropical country :) Wow yum! Will be back with friends :)", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Alex and Jose at the outdoor bar totally made our experience!! We enjoyed the Comal Swizzle and whole cod! Felt like in a different tropical country :) Wow yum! Will be back with friends :)", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Raye Twist", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102451959991998288636/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_ot15i9MpifAfndt0eRZM0YxWvWwxYp0mA5Rduw1rSITC7pM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-07-13T01:50:23.589478550Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xrelYxTkxhbWM1YWxSYVdFeDFjbHBHWjBsUWRIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xrelYxTkxhbWM1YWxSYVdFeDFjbHBHWjBsUWRIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857e9e893c79c3:0x5b6e97d44d0b2925"}, {"name": "places/ChIJw3k8iZ5-hYARJSkLTdSXbls/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUMyNXRhMzl3RRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We had some excellent food at Comal. We sat at the bar and got an up close and personal view of the well-run kitchen and its highly trained team. The food isn't exactly 100% traditional Mexican cuisine, but it's still firmly grounded in it. We had the carnitas tacos with citrus and the duck enchiladas as entrees and both were even better than we expected. The guacamole and three salsas paired with their chips were also delicious. We had a small snafu with the service, but after pointing it out, our server immediately corrected it to our satisfaction, which is all one can expect. All in all, our meal was a treat and we felt this place was deserving of its reputation and Bib Gourmand listing. We will be back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We had some excellent food at Comal. We sat at the bar and got an up close and personal view of the well-run kitchen and its highly trained team. The food isn't exactly 100% traditional Mexican cuisine, but it's still firmly grounded in it. We had the carnitas tacos with citrus and the duck enchiladas as entrees and both were even better than we expected. The guacamole and three salsas paired with their chips were also delicious. We had a small snafu with the service, but after pointing it out, our server immediately corrected it to our satisfaction, which is all one can expect. All in all, our meal was a treat and we felt this place was deserving of its reputation and Bib Gourmand listing. We will be back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jason Matsumoto", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114404093772526631940/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVpqUOaupLJRSNbyBEZXp5m9AyPOnXG5C5BATHDZI4drs1b4-gGEw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2022-04-19T21:38:39.045958Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUMyNXRhMzl3RRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUMyNXRhMzl3RRAB!2m1!1s0x80857e9e893c79c3:0x5b6e97d44d0b2925"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJw3k8iZ5-hYARJSkLTdSXbls/photos/AWCwydg1cEoJbjfly17xyFvgf44L13SaXwF8e5SaJ6trEPkZeK3bThNF5-MjkPWDmllbL89FxF0NQvDOro_LI9ZjMRk3wCAzkU8KYNBaM_q5Wvo2P9MvCQKb3HuA62d7l8DQn6rDKor18Jeb8Khc178T2Rfcz9S3EK1OTJI10ASBes0tVZg2tOwU_5OGa6K1hwgvl7qya0MNyDb-L5DOwWpJbwmUwFC4_eXy8h2aiMi1R5ZIu9bP70ZGTYBwcrMZSQLO5T6r70Bqve59JxN4-5Li8Wt060y8af7nQKjZSkvYeGCVlroSoKBUxrNnV-AnodzgOiXxF1Kt9FWTEVTJ1-F4hSIT0DNgcDhoBQiiobpLHeqkHJ90HQwE0LHmOvL7kGtrmZPhD6_oRFJUWTI6AMZkhyQp3V1rnM3EmF7OLgOxZ6wv3II", "widthPx": 617, "heightPx": 464, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Comal", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/102861950512160837742", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkS8-gYMjHFYzoCdKhzhTWvY-ofYU-zgxcUnIER269PPyWIg=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIHM